Package: smplot2
Type: Package
Title: Creating and Annotating a Composite Plot in 'ggplot2'
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Seung Hyun (Sam)",
      family = "Min",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
